more than enough!

68
00:04:26,875 --> 00:04:29,000
Any chance I get,
I'll picture them together!

69
00:04:29,083 --> 00:04:33,208
This is the way I live
my life and I am not ashamed!

70
00:04:33,291 --> 00:04:37,583
Even classmates are no exception
to the whims of my fantasy.

71
00:04:37,666 --> 00:04:39,791
Don't you think Nanashima
looks a lot like Shion

72
00:04:39,875 --> 00:04:41,291
from <i>Mirage Saga</i> ?

73
00:04:41,375 --> 00:04:43,958
[NAKANO] Ooh, in that
bad boy sorta way, right?

74
00:04:44,041 --> 00:04:44,750
[SERINUMA]
Yeah!

75
00:04:44,833 --> 00:04:46,166
[giggling]

76
00:04:46,250 --> 00:04:48,333
Pardon me. Serinuma.

77
00:04:48,416 --> 00:04:52,041
If you're feeling better now,
would you stop hogging the bed?

78
00:04:52,125 --> 00:04:54,250
