226
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:56,875
[TAKURO yells]
That's freaky!

227
00:09:58,750 --> 00:10:01,000
[SERINUMA]
Is this real?

228
00:10:01,083 --> 00:10:02,958
I feel so different.

229
00:10:03,041 --> 00:10:06,333
It's strange...
but what can I do?

230
00:10:06,416 --> 00:10:08,625
